  <brief_title>Precision Immunology to Determine the Immune Response in Patients With COVID-19</brief_title>
  <official_title>Precision Immunology Approach to Better Understand the Divergent Host Responses Towards Infection With SARS-CoV-2</official_title>
  <sponsors>
